&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Tucson shifts into robot mode and presses his wings tightly against his
&gt; body, while swiftly moving into the tunnel on silent and agile limbs. His
&gt; shoulders do touch the tunnel and scrape them just a slight but realizing it
&gt; quickly, he remembers his training and puts it to use.  He gets low to the
&gt; ground and manages to just clear the hole in the tunnel.  It was lucky for
&gt; him that the dragon head shifted to his chest plate upon transformation.
&gt; Yet his keen ears remain in place on his helmet.  Like his sonar receptors,
&gt; they are extremely sharp at picking up the slightest sounds.  He keeps them
&gt; on high alert at all times.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; I hear movement.  And it&#39;s above us, coming in our direction.  Shhh..  We
&gt; have to stop moving for a moment, scramble our signatures and dim our
&gt; optics.  What they can&#39;t detect will be to our advantage.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; Tucson quickly does what Master Yokitron had taught him.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; it&#39;s an old Ninjabot trick.  Master Yokitron taught it to all his
&gt; students.&quot;

&lt;NEW&gt;

BIG CONVOY grunted from his position above TUSCON, &quot;It&#39;s the guards
coming through on the indpection I told you about.&quot; Carefully he
closed the cover to the hole that had been dug, it made no sound
except for a click as it closed and locked.

Once it was closed even TUSCON&#39;s enhanced hearing could hear nothing
through it.

&quot;Go on down.&quot; CONVOY said quietly. &quot;The floor paneling of our cells is
armor plated.&quot;

&quot;Yeah.&quot; NIGHT VIPER said from below TUSCON, &quot;It took us about a month
to dig &#39;em through&quot;

BIG CONVOY nodded, &quot;They should muffle our sounds and signatures
enough for the moment, but we need to keep moving.&quot;

VIPER chuckled, &quot;And the image inducers should fool those idiots for a while.&quot;

